  <brief_title>Decitabine in Treating Patients With Melanoma or Other Advanced Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Study of the Biologic and Clinical Effects of 5-AZA-2'Deoxycytidine (DAC) in Patients With Advanced Malignancies</official_title>
